      "text": "1、2、3、4……1、2、3、4……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブに向けて練習にも熱が入っているな\n……しかし、いつもより動きが硬い気がするが……",
      "startTime": 9.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、調子が良くないようだが何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 15.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、少し疲れが溜まっているのかもしれません",
      "startTime": 19.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "今度、学校でクリスマス会をやるんですが\n私も生徒会長として手伝うことになったんです",
      "startTime": 27.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの練習、生徒会の通常業務、期末テストの勉強\nそれにクリスマス会の準備で休む暇がなくて……",
      "startTime": 37.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。あまり無理しないようにな\nもし俺に手伝えることがあれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 45.6000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_06_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "手伝えることですか？\nでは、一つお尋ねしてもよろしいでしょうか",
      "startTime": 51.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}